<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤١٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمَعْنَاهُ، وَزَادَ <span class="c2">«فِي صَلَاةِ الْجُمُعَةِ بِسُورَةِ الْجُمُعَةِ،<span class="c5"> وَ:</span> <span class="c3">{إِذَا جَاءَكَ الْمُنَافِقُونَ}</span>»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>